{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-blog-post-jsx","path":"/Neovim/24-neovim-and-java/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"id":"a6d93c3a-e8de-5e2d-bf09-fa0abdb68a6a","html":"<h2>Current State of Java + Neovim</h2>\n<p><strong>Available:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/nvim-treesitter/nvim-treesitter\">Treesitter highlighting</a></li>\n<li>Goto definition</li>\n<li>Goto references</li>\n<li>Formatting</li>\n<li>Diagnostics</li>\n<li>Hover</li>\n<li>Refactor/Rename</li>\n<li>Search files (FZF)</li>\n<li>Search text (FZF)</li>\n<li>Quickfix</li>\n<li>Lombok</li>\n<li>Configuration in <code class=\"language-text\">coc-settings.json</code></li>\n</ul>\n<p><strong>Difficult to Implement:</strong></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Debugging</li>\n</ul>\n<p>* This can be done but in my opinion it's difficult to get setup, if you'd like to look further into it checkout the following:</p>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/mfussenegger/nvim-dap\">nvim-dap</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/puremourning/vimspector\">vimspector</a></li>\n</ul>\n<h3>Note</h3>\n<p>You will need to have CoC installed I have a blog post and video for installing CoC here:</p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OXEVhnY621M\">YouTube Video</a></p>\n<p><a href=\"https://www.chrisatmachine.com/Neovim/04-vim-coc/\">Blog Post</a></p>\n<h2>Install</h2>\n<p><strong>Treesitter</strong></p>\n<p><em>You will need Neovim>=0.5</em></p>\n<ul>\n<li>Install with VimPlug</li>\n</ul>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      Plug 'nvim-treesitter/nvim-treesitter'\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<p>Add this to your <code class=\"language-text\">init.vim</code></p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      require'nvim-treesitter.configs'.setup {\n  ensure_installed = \"maintained\", -- one of \"all\", \"maintained\" (parsers with maintainers), or a list of languages\n  highlight = {\n    enable = true,              -- false will disable the whole extension\n  },\n}\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<p><strong>coc-java</strong></p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      :CocInstall coc-java\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<p><strong>Lombok</strong></p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      sudo mkdir /usr/local/share/lombok\n\nsudo wget https://projectlombok.org/downloads/lombok.jar -O /usr/local/share/lombok/lombok.jar\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Commands</h2>\n<p>Here are a bunch of commands to get the behavior of this video:</p>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      <Plug>(coc-codeaction)              \" line action\n<Plug>(coc-definition)              \" definition\n<Plug>(coc-references)              \" references\n<Plug>(coc-type-definition)         \" type definition\n<Plug>(coc-rename)                  \" rename\n<Plug>(coc-declaration)             \" declaration\n<Plug>(coc-implementation)          \" implementation\n<Plug>(coc-format)                  \" format\n<Plug>(coc-fix-current)             \" quickfix\n<Plug>(coc-codelens-action)         \" code lens\n<Plug>(coc-diagnostic-next)         \" next diagnostic\n<Plug>(coc-diagnostic-next-error)   \" next error\n:CocList diagnostics                \" diagnostics\n:CocList outline                    \" search outline\n:CocList -I symbols                 \" references\n:CocUpdate                          \" update CoC\n:CocDisable                         \" disable CoC\n:CocEnable                          \" enable CoC\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Configuration</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><code class=\"language-text\">coc-settings.json</code></li>\n</ul>\n<code-fence lang=\"null\" null>\n    <textarea vue-slot=\"code\">\n      // codelens\n\"codeLens.enable\": true,\n\"java.referencesCodeLens.enabled\": true,\n\"java.jdt.ls.vmargs\": \"-javaagent:/usr/local/share/lombok.jar\",\n// \"java.jdt.ls.vmargs\": \"-javaagent:/usr/local/share/lombok.jar -Xbootclasspath/a:/usr/local/share/lombok.jar\", // for older versions of Java\n    </textarea>\n    </code-fence>\n  \n<h2>Repo Links</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://github.com/neoclide/coc-java\">coc-java</a>\n<a href=\"https://github.com/nvim-treesitter/nvim-treesitter\">treesitter</a></p>","excerpt":"Current State of Java + Neovim Available: Treesitter highlighting Goto definition Goto references Formatting Diagnostics Hover Refactorâ€¦","frontmatter":{"title":"Java in Neovim","tags":["neovim"],"image":{"childImageSharp":{"resize":{"src":"/static/bec5f0551a6f0debb05ead8aeff27759/a8734/Neovim_Java.png"},"fluid":{"base64":"data:image/png;base64,","aspectRatio":1.7747747747747749,"src":"/static/bec5f0551a6f0debb05ead8aeff27759/5134e/Neovim_Java.png","srcSet":"/static/bec5f0551a6f0debb05ead8aeff27759/06f82/Neovim_Java.png 197w,\n/static/bec5f0551a6f0debb05ead8aeff27759/da7d7/Neovim_Java.png 393w,\n/static/bec5f0551a6f0debb05ead8aeff27759/5134e/Neovim_Java.png 786w,\n/static/bec5f0551a6f0debb05ead8aeff27759/7a32a/Neovim_Java.png 1179w,\n/static/bec5f0551a6f0debb05ead8aeff27759/e4d72/Neovim_Java.png 1280w","sizes":"(max-width: 786px) 100vw, 786px"}}}}}},"pageContext":{"slug":"/Neovim/24-neovim-and-java/","prev":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/Neovim/25-vimspector/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"Vimspector (for Java)","tags":["neovim"]}}},"next":{"node":{"fields":{"slug":"/Opinion/java-is-stupid-and-i-hate-it/"},"frontmatter":{"title":"I hate Java (and Spring)","tags":["opinion"]}}}}},"staticQueryHashes":["3649515864"]}